{
  "texts": [
    "Questions with fewer than 14 words are padded with zero vectors.",
    "A question embedding is then generated using a GRU applied to the word embeddings.",
    "An LSTM-based attention mechanism considers both the question vector and the visual representations making up the nodes of the scene graph.",
    "This module considers previously attended areas when exploring new visual features.",
    "Finally, an LSTM-based language generator is used to generate the final answer."
  ]
}